  <trk>
    <name>From Croix de Culet via the Col de Cou to Champéry</name>
    <desc>Panorama-rich hike to a dramatic border crossing high above the Val d’Illiez. Besides a scenic gondola ride, alpine huts and mountain restaurants, the idyllic plateau of Barme awaits you.</desc>
